Package: epinowcast
Title: Nowcast Right Censored Epidemiological Counts
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Sam Abbott",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "sam.abbott@lshtm.ac.uk",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8057-8037"))
Description: Tools to enable flexible and efficient nowcasting of  right
    censored epidemiological counts using a semi-mechanistic method with
    adjustment available for both day of reference and day of report effects. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://samabbott.co.uk/epinowcast/,
    https://github.com/seabbs/epinowcast/
